<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2006-09-12.11.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80050" speakername="Mr Adam Ingram (South of Scotland) (SNP)" spid="S2W-27811" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-06/wa0912.htm#5">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive what the incidence of mental illness and mental health problems is among students and what trends have been identified in relation to this issue.</p>

